room_title: Escape room "Hitler and The Spear of Destiny" by Escape History in Warren
room_description: Your team have snuck into Adolf Hitler's office in search of the legendary Spear of Destiny, his most prized possession. The Spear is said to grant the beholder invincibility, explaining why the Third Reich has been so powerful. You need to find the spear and escape within the hour to seal victory for the allies. If not, the German's will more than likely win WWII and history will be changed forever!
